query:
INSERT INTO http_responses (
                id,
                request_id,
                workspace_id,
                elapsed,
                elapsed_headers,
                url,
                status,
                status_reason,
                content_length,
                body_path,
                headers,
                version,
                remote_addr
            )
            VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?);
